Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.40,0:18:52.82,Default CN,,0,0,0,,Black！White！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.30,0:18:55.97,Default JP,,0,0,0,,力を合わせるポポ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.30,0:18:55.97,Default CN,,0,0,0,,将力量结合起来吧！
